<BRK/>
<TXT>Identify the safety and health aspects of lead-based paint removal, prepared in accordance with Section 
<SRF>02 83 00</SRF> LEAD REMEDIATION.</TXT><BRK/>
<BRK/></SPT>
]<TAI OPT="NAVY">[<SPT><TTL>Lead Compliance Plan</TTL><BRK/>
