<NTE><BRK/>
<AST/><BRK/>
<NPR>NOTE:<TAI OPT="NAVY">  The sentences referring to ESAMS are  tailored for use on NAVY projects.</TAI><TAI OPT="ARMY,NASA">
  The sentences referring to USACE Form 3394 are tailored for use on ARMY and 
NASA projects.</TAI></NPR><BRK/>
<AST/><BRK/></NTE>
<BRK/>
